Nomura Securities International, Inc. Key Developments

Nomura Appoints Christopher Marai as Managing Director and Senior Analyst in the Firm's U.S. Equity Research Department
Sep 27 16
Nomura announced that Christopher Marai, Ph.D., has joined as a Managing Director and senior analyst, covering Biotechnology in the firm's U.S. Equity Research department. Mr. Marai will be based in San Francisco and joins Nomura from Oppenheimer & Co., where he was most recently a Managing Director and top-ranked senior analyst covering the Biotechnology sector.


Nomura Securities International, Inc. Presents at 22nd Annual ABS East Conference, Sep-19-2016 11:15 AM
Sep 15 16
Nomura Securities International, Inc. Presents at 22nd Annual ABS East Conference, Sep-19-2016 11:15 AM. Venue: Fontainebleau Miami Beach, 4441 Collins Avenue, Miami Beach, FL 33140, United States. Speakers: Paul Nikodem, Managing Director-Head SP Research.


Nomura Securities International, Inc. Presents at UNC Alternative Investments Conference, Mar-23-2016 04:15 PM
Mar 22 16
Nomura Securities International, Inc. Presents at UNC Alternative Investments Conference, Mar-23-2016 04:15 PM. Venue: The Carolina Inn, Chapel Hill, NC, United States. Speakers: Aaron Tavel, Managing Director.


